section#section-contact
  h1.section-title Contact Us
  h2.page-title Contact Us
  p To help you get your quote quicker, please be as detailed as possible when you fill out the message form. You will receive
    |a reply from us shortly to setup a free one hour consultation at the site of your mural. After the consulation, we will provide
    |a quote instantly and before you know it, your walls be beautifully transformed!
  small All fields are required unless specified.
  form(method="post", id="contact-form",action="php/send-email.php")
    .row
      .input-wrap
        input(type="text",placeholder="Name",name="form-name",data-required)
      .input-wrap
        input(type="text",placeholder="Email",name="form-email",data-required,data-type="email")
    .row
      .input-wrap
        input(type="text",placeholder="Phone Number (optional)",name="form-phone",data-error-message="Please enter valid phone number")
      .input-wrap
        select(data-required,name="form-interest")
          option(value) I'm interested in...
          option(value="Murals") Murals
          option(value="Portraits") Portraits
          option(value="Fine Art") Fine Art
          option(value="Art Lessons") Art Lessons
          option(value="Other") Other
    .row
      .input-wrap
        textarea(placeholder="Your message (500 Characters Max)",name="form-message",data-required,data-maxlength="500")
    .row
      input(type="submit", value="Send Message", id="submit-btn") Send Message
  div.cl
